    <title>The Social Construction of Race during Reconstruction</title>
    <updated>2025-02-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Anjali Adukia, Richard Hornbeck, Daniel Keniston &amp; Benjamin Lualdi</name>
